According to the requirement of information integration for the CNC equipments, remote monitoring and management system for CNC based on Rich Internet Application (RIA) is developed. The structure and key technology of the system are introduced in detail. Serial port servers are used to realize the network connection of the CNC equipments. Based on RIA structure, the system achieves remote transmission of NC programs, real-time monitoring and analyzing the running status of CNC equipments. With more convenient information processing and more accurate equipment condition mastering, the productivity can be improved effectively.